FREALLY ANTI-VIRUS — RUST CRATE ATTRIBUTIONS
================================================

This file lists every Rust crate compiled into Freally Anti-Virus,
together with its version, license, and (where the upstream license
requires) the full text of that license. Generated automatically by
`cargo about generate about.hbs` per `about.toml`. Do not hand-edit;
regenerate at release time.

Each section below names a license, the third-party crates that
ship under it, and the full license text. Crates whose license is
already captured by an earlier section appear under that section's
"Used by" list, not separately.

